{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f5234c2887","title":"在表扬牙灭白崇禧主力的部队的电报上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"99cc4df205","index":0,"year":1949,"month":10,"day":13,"articleId":"f5234c2887"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"00f1701bf5","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5234c2887","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"白崇禧，1949年4月被任命为国民党政府华中军政长官公署长官。"},{"id":"284ff5c25c","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5234c2887","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指林彪、邓子恢、谭政等1949年10月12日表扬中国人民解放军第四十军、四十一军和四十九军歼灭白崇禧主力的电报。"},{"id":"d9d660d818","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5234c2887","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"程颂云，即程潜，原国民党政府军将领，1949年8月与陈明仁率部在长沙起义。当时任中央人民政府委员、湖南人民军政委员会主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2f6322e1a2","type":"title","text":"在表扬死灭白崇德力的部队的电报则上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5234c2887"},{"id":"00f1701bf5","type":"paragraph","text":"程颂云先生阅。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5234c2887"},{"id":"284ff5c25c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5234c2887"},{"id":"d9d660d818","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十三日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5234c2887"},{"id":"0965b3d382","type":"paragraph","text":"被轩灭者是七军两个师及四十八军两个师，地点在祁阳以北。消灭这些部队时白崇禧坐视不救，自己退到桂林，各军退到东安、零陵、冷水滩一带，听任七军四八军苦战四天被歼干净。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5234c2887"}],"page":{"id":"2dace97376","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"f5234c2887","start":411,"end":411}}}},"__N_SSG":true}